"{\"uid\": \"cbsnews.com-news-suni-lee-2024-paris-olympics-gymnast-i-gave-it-my-all\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Watch CBS News  August 5, 2024 / 2:54 PM EDT/ CBS News  Two-time OlympianSuni Leeis proud of her performance at theParis Olympics, saying \\\"I gave it my all, and that's all that matters.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9986044484070979, \"rank\": 0.0013974958552248125, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 54, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9986044484070979, \"rank\": 0.0013974958552248125, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old Team USA gymnast won bronze in the uneven bars final on Sunday - her third medal of the 2024 Paris Games.\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Monday, she fell during the balance beam final.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 358, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not even think that I would make it this far,\\\" Lee told CBS News on Monday.\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9958990581452102, \"rank\": 0.0039025955331304265, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"score\": 0.9986044484070979, \"rank\": 0.0013974958552248125, \"text\": \"CBS News\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CBS_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I am trying to give myself a little bit of grace and be like, OK, we did not even think that we would be at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So making it to the final was just kind of a bonus.\\\"\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, Lee was diagnosed with two kidney diseases that put her training schedule on hold and her Olympic dreams into question.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 632, \"end\": 635, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9958990581452102, \"rank\": 0.0039025955331304265, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But theMinnesota nativelaunched a comeback of Olympic proportions.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud of myself, because I never would have thought that I got to this point in my life right now,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 938, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for what the future of U.S. gymnastics looks like, Lee is feeling pretty good about that, too.\", \"from\": 940, \"to\": 1037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.9958990581452102, \"rank\": 0.0039025955331304265, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said that watchingSimone Biles\\\"has definitely shown that nothing is impossible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like it's just going to keep evolving and being absolutely amazing,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1125, \"to\": 1211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles, a 27-year-old 11-time Olympicmedalist, returned to the Olympic stage this year after the\\\"twisties\\\"- where gymnasts lose their place in the air - pushed her to drop out of the 2020 Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last week, Biles became the first American gymnast towin the Olympic individual all-around competition twice.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9957474745858668, \"rank\": 0.00418560084011318, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2024 CBS Interactive Inc. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CBS Interactive Inc.\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paramount_Streaming\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(03:16)  Copyright \\u00a92025 CBS Interactive Inc. All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": []}]}"